primary.context: Caller wanted to verify the address and owner name on file for their maintenance bill.
primary.detail: The agent verified the caller and provided the address and owner name associated with the contract.

steps: Agent performed account lookup via phone number.
Agent verified caller identity (name and state).
Agent provided address on file upon request.
Agent provided owner name and contract details upon request.
Caller confirmed no further needs and call ended.

clarifications.note: Agent asked for spelling when name didn't match.

actions.detail: Verified caller Valerie Creo from New Jersey.

insights.summary: The caller successfully verified their account and obtained specific contract details (address and owner name) regarding their maintenance bill.
